node.text:
The floodgates are open once again. Singapore has now transitioned into Phase 2 / re-opening of the economy. This is definitely something that many of us are looking forward to. At the same time, it is also important to continue to stay safe and maintain social responsibility. 😷

Now would you rather be cooped up at home or be stuck in a traffic jam?
